All Implemented Interfaces:
NodeVisitor<SoyNode,Void>
public class PrependNamespacesVisitor
extends AbstractSoyNodeVisitor<Void>

Visitor for prepending namespaces to the names for TemplateNodes and CallNodes (so that the resulting names are all full names instead of partial names).

Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).

AbstractNodeVisitor.exec(N) should be called on a full parse tree. The name attributes of 'template' and 'call' nodes may be modified. There is no return value.
